## Examples  
 The following code example resets the geometric transform of `pgBrush` to identity. It is assumed that `myPath` is an existing <xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.GraphicsPath>.  

```csharp  
PathGradientBrush pgBrush = new PathGradientBrush(myPath);  
 pgBrush.ResetTransform();  
```
